data.description:
HUGE PRICE REDUCTION for this BEAUTIFUL HOME!!  PLUS a Voluntary HOA ($50/yr) & NO CCD!  New roof 1/2022. Upgraded SS Frig & SS double oven & SS microwave. Brick & cementitious siding exterior. Full exterior & interior of home painted in 8/2023, to include doors & trim. Fully fenced. INSIDE LAUNDRY ROOM. 7/2023 upgraded to luxury vinyl flooring throughout whole home w/exception of new upgraded carpet in all bedrooms. New ceiling fixtures/fans/lavatories.  Ranch style beauty in the quiet Middleburg neighborhood of McCrae, one of the most quiet & serene neighborhoods in N FL, plus an owner car park a trailer/boat/food truck at their residence & AVOID additional STORAGE COSTS!   Expansive 119' driveway, 2-car garage, welcomes you & your guests, providing the place & space for all the fun outdoor activities your friends & family enjoy. Making your way inside it feels like 'home'- the recently refreshed space & new floors throughout make coming home after a long day, a breath of fresh air! The beautiful fireplace grabs your attention and keeps your family warm on those chilly days. Continuing outside, you'll notice the large, fenced in backyard that is spacious enough for all your fun, family activities, that also gives you the privacy to create the backyard oasis of your dreams.

This home offers a 3-way split floor plan, giving everyone a place of their own. Off the family room, the master suite offers tray ceilings, double windows, two walk-in-closets, double sinks, and a garden tub; no need to share here, whether getting ready in the morning or winding down after a long day!

There are two bedrooms in the front wing to the left as you pass the formal dining room separated by a full bath, and the fourth bedroom, located off the kitchen, faces the backyard.
Don't wait to take advantage of this perfect abode, the home you have been looking for has arrived!
All measurements to be verified by the buyer.
